"Dil Khoya Khoya Gumsum", a Song  of  the Bollywood Film  of  1988  produced and directed by Parkash Mehra. Singer of the Song is Indian Legend Asha Bhosle   Originally sung by Iranian Singer (Googoosh).Composed by Ustad Zaland  or Zoland 1960.
